- Average Entropy: {{ $json.behaviorMetrics.file_operations.entropy_analysis.avg_entropy }}
- Entropy Increase Events: {{ $json.behaviorMetrics.file_operations.entropy_analysis.entropy_increase_count }}

**Process Activity:**
- Active Processes: {{ JSON.stringify($json.behaviorMetrics.process_activity.unique_processes) }}
