2. Classify attack type (crypto-locker, wiper, ransomware-as-a-service, or false positive)
3. Identify ransomware family if possible (LockBit, BlackCat, Royal, Play, etc.)
4. Determine confidence level (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)
5. Recommend immediate action (ISOLATE_IMMEDIATELY, MONITOR_CLOSELY, or NO_ACTION)
